Job Details
Bookings Manager needed for British Domestic Maintenance Company.Ideal candidates will have:-- Qualified British tradesman experience (Plumber, HVAC, Electrician, Carpenter)–Candidate will need to be able to talk knowledgably over the phone about a wide range of domestic maintenance issues with our clients.- Excellent communication skills.- In depth understanding of good customer service.- Knowledge of live job scheduling.- Experience of on-site customer meetings & quoting.- Ability to resolve HR and customer service issues.- Ability to participate and provide specialist technical training for our staff as required.- Real estate and developer approvals experience preferred.- UAE (or UK) manual driving license.You will receive:-- A good salary- Transport- A positive working environment in a growing and dynamic company- Annual return flight ticket to UK- Employment visa- 24 working days holiday a year
Requirements
British (UK) Candidates preferred.
Already located in the UAE (no UK based candidates).
British Tradesman- Plumber, Electrician, A/C Engineer etc.
